Template: debian-secure-boot/passphrase
Type: password
Description: Enter the passphrase for secure boot private keys:
 The debian-secure-boot package was used to generate private keys for signing
 boot files, such as bootloaders and kernels. Enter the passphrase for these
 keys so that the boot files can be signed.

